{"type":"message","id":"0d069c20","parentId":"6e7b80bd","timestamp":"2026-06-14T01:40:51.596Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**步骤 4：检查速度档位映射问题 - 查看 ISAPI actual speed 返回**\n\n问题 2 描述说速度1和7实际移动完全一样。让我检查后端代码的速度映射逻辑是否正确。代码中已经有正确的映射表 `{1: 14, 2: 28, 3: 43, 4: 57, 5: 71, 6: 86, 7: 100}`。\n\n但问题可能在于：\n1. ISAPI continuous_move 的 pan/tilt 参数计算问题\n2. 或者设备本身忽略这些值\n\n让我检查 continuous_move 的参数传递："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-2b0777df199e4904a54d1a229abbdd5e","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1148,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":95445,"output":178,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95623,"cost":{"input":0.095445,"output":0.0005696000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0960146}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781401242681,"responseId":"cht000dcfaa@dx19ec3c9d054ba5d322"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4a2117b6","parentId":"0d069c20","timestamp":"2026-06-14T01:40:51.603Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-2b0777df199e4904a54d1a229abbdd5e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def continuous_move(self, pan: float = 0, tilt: float = 0, zoom: float = 0, focus: float = 0) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"连续移动 PTZ。\r\n\r\n        官方 ISAPI 1.0 格式: pan/tilt/zoom 直接传速度值，范围 -100 到 100。\r\n        参考: doc/ptzhelper_source.py continuous_move() - 直接传值不做映射。\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        # 官方 ISAPI 1.0 格式：直接传值，不做映射\r\n        pan_speed = int(pan)\r\n        tilt_speed = int(tilt)\r\n        zoom_speed = int(zoom)\r\n        focus_speed = int(focus)\r\n\r\n        # 官方格式：<PTZData><pan>{pan}</pan><tilt>{tilt}</tilt><zoom>{zoom}</zoom></PTZData>\r\n        xml = f'<PTZData><pan>{pan_speed}</pan><tilt>{tilt_speed}</tilt><zoom>{zoom_speed}</zoom></PTZData>'\r\n        result = self.client.put(f\"{self._ptz_base()}/continuous\", xml)\r\n        return result.status_code == 200\r\n\r\n    def stop_move(self) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"停止所有移动（PTZ + Focus）。\"\"\"\r\n        # 停止 PTZ 移动\r\n        ptz_stop = self.continuous_move(0, 0, 0, 0)\r\n        # 停止 Focus 移动\r\n        focus_stop = self.focus_stop()\r\n        return ptz_stop and focus_stop\r\n\r\n    def continuous_move_duration(self, pan: float, tilt: float, duration: float) -> list[dict]:\r\n        positions = []\r\n        if not self.continuous_move(pan=pan, tilt=tilt, focus=0):\r\n            return positions\r\n        start = time.time()\r\n\n[1730 more lines in file. Use offset=1178 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781401251603}}
{"type":"message","id":"94593b36","parentId":"4a2117b6","timestamp":"2026-06-14T01:40:59.873Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我发现问题了！在 `ptz_move` 方法中：\n\n```python\npan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed)\ntilt = int(tilt_val * isapi_speed)\n```\n\n但是 `pan_val` 和 `tilt_val` 来自 `DIRECTION_MAP`，它们的值是 -1, 0, 1 这样的方向值。最终传给 `continuous_move` 的是 `方向值 * isapi_speed`。\n\n问题是：**ISAPI 的 continuous 端点接收的是速度值，而不是方向值乘以速度**。\n\n让我查看 DIRECTION_MAP 的定义："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_32dc74acb19842118414a3c1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1376,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":111004,"output":170,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111174,"cost":{"input":0.11100399999999999,"output":0.000544,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.111548}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781401251605,"responseId":"cht000d7399@dx19ec3c9f1cdb9cb212"}}
{"type":"message","id":"011837f1","parentId":"94593b36","timestamp":"2026-06-14T01:40:59.880Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_32dc74acb19842118414a3c1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def __init__(self) -> None:\r\n        LOG.log(\"info\", \"PTZManager 初始化完成\")\r\n        from src.config_paths import CONFIG_DIR as _CONFIG_DIR\r\n        self.config = ConfigManager(\r\n            local_path=_CONFIG_DIR / \"local.json\",\r\n            ptz_path=_CONFIG_DIR / \"ptz_config.json\",\r\n        )\r\n        self.recorder = CSVRecorder()\r\n        self._clients: dict[str, ISAPIClient] = {}\r\n        self._controllers: dict[str, PTZController] = {}\r\n        # {ip: {\"username\": ..., \"password\": ..., \"port\": ...}}\r\n        self._credentials: dict[str, dict[str, str | int]] = {}\r\n        # {mac: device_info_dict} - SADP 发现缓存\r\n        self._discovered: dict[str, SADPDevice] = {}\r\n        # {ip: {\"track_id\": int, \"started_at\": float, \"started_at_iso\": str, \"channel\": int}} - ISAPI 录像状态\r\n        self._recording_state: dict[str, dict[str, int | float | str]] = {}\r\n        self._credentials = {}\r\n        self._load_saved_credentials()\r\n        self._ftp_config: dict = {}\r\n\r\n    def get_config(self) -> ConfigManager:\r\n        return self.config\r\n\r\n    # ================================================================\r\n    #  SADP 发现 & 设备管理\r\n    # ================================================================\r\n\r\n    def discover_devices(self, bind_ip: str = \"0.0.0.0\") -> list[dict]:\r\n        \"\"\"执行 SADP 发现并返回设备列表（dict 格式）。\r\n\r\n\n[1502 more lines in file. Use offset=1406 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781401259880}}
