{"type":"message","id":"b666a643","parentId":"bc18b4c9","timestamp":"2026-06-14T01:41:22.204Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"问题找到了！`DIRECTION_MAP` 使用的是固定值 100，然后后面代码又乘以 `isapi_speed`：\n\n```python\npan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]  # (0, 100) 或 (-100, 0) 等\n...\npan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed)  # 0 * 57 = 0, 100 * 57 = 5700 (!)\n```\n\n这是错误的！应该是：\n```python\npan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed / 100)  # 归一化后再乘速度\n```\n\n或者修改 DIRECTION_MAP 为 -1, 0, 1：\n\n让我修复这个问题："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9704b0802028459f9cd3c0a3","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    DIRECTION_MAP = {\n        \"up\":       (0, 1),\n        \"down\":     (0, -1),\n        \"left\":     (-1, 0),\n        \"right\":    (1, 0),\n        \"up-left\":  (-1, 1),\n        \"up-right\": (1, 1),\n        \"down-left\": (-1, -1),\n        \"down-right\": (1, -1),\n    }","oldText":"    DIRECTION_MAP = {\n        \"up\":       (0, 100),\n        \"down\":     (0, -100),\n        \"left\":     (-100, 0),\n        \"right\":    (100, 0),\n        \"up-left\":  (-100, 100),\n        \"up-right\": (100, 100),\n        \"down-left\": (-100, -100),\n        \"down-right\": (100, -100),\n    }"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":112032,"output":432,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112464,"cost":{"input":0.11203199999999999,"output":0.0013824000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1134144}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781401270754,"responseId":"cht000d6ef8@dx19ec3ca3c39b8ab282"}}
