{"type":"message","id":"047121ce","parentId":"11e13dd9","timestamp":"2026-06-14T01:42:27.539Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我需要修改 `disableImageControls` 函数，使其同时禁用 PTZ 控制、媒体操作、跟踪控制区域。让我重写这个函数："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-a86cdc429d6a4406a152bde0d290918d","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":"[{\"newText\": \"// v6.20 + v7.0: 禁用所有控制区域（PTZ + 媒体 + 跟踪 + 画面）\\nfunction disableImageControls(reason) {\\n    // 禁用画面控制控件\\n    var controls = [\\n        'consoleBrightness', 'consoleContrast', 'consoleSaturation', 'consoleSharpness',\\n        'wbMode', 'wbRed', 'wbBlue', 'dnrSpatial', 'dnrTemporal',\\n        'exposureMode', 'shutterSpeed', 'irisLevel',\\n        'infoOsdSwitch', 'ptzOsdSwitch'\\n    ];\\n    controls.forEach(function(id) {\\n        var el = document.getElementById(id);\\n        if (el) {\\n            el.disabled = true;\\n            el.style.opacity = '0.5';\\n            el.style.cursor = 'not-allowed';\\n        }\\n    });\\n    \\n    // v7.0: 禁用 PTZ 控制按钮\\n    var ptzButtons = document.querySelectorAll('#ptzControlSection .ptz-btn');\\n    ptzButtons.forEach(function(btn) {\\n        if (!btn.classList.contains('center')) {\\n            btn.disabled = true;\\n            btn.style.opacity = '0.5';\\n            btn.style.cursor = 'not-allowed';\\n            btn.style.pointerEvents = 'none';\\n        }\\n    });\\n    var ptzControlBtns = document.querySelectorAll('#ptzControlSection .btn');\\n    ptzControlBtns.forEach(function(btn) {\\n        btn.disabled = true;\\n        btn.style.opacity = '0.5';\\n        btn.style.cursor = 'not-allowed';\\n    });\\n    \\n    // v7.0: 禁用媒体操作按钮\\n    var mediaButtons = ['btnConsoleSnapshot', 'btnConsoleRecordStart', 'btnConsoleRecordStop', 'btnLiveStackStart', 'btnLiveStackStop', 'btnLiveStackSave'];\\n    mediaButtons.forEach(function(id) {\\n        var el = document.getElementById(id);\\n        if (el) {\\n            el.disabled = true;\\n            el.style.opa