{"type":"message","id":"bb21e9f0","parentId":"29b5f691","timestamp":"2026-06-14T02:24:26.984Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"问题可能是 `I_InsertOBJECTPlugin` 只能调用一次。让我检查是否需要防止重复初始化。同时检查 wasmLogout 是否在多次调用时出问题。\n\n让我检查 wasmLogout 函数，确保它不会破坏 WASM 容器："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dd3f7c8f211b4a74aaa407c2","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":2248,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":83006,"output":97,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83103,"cost":{"input":0.083006,"output":0.0003104,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0833164}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781403858084,"responseId":"cht000d507e@dx19ec3f1c164ba60352"}}
