{"type":"message","id":"deda6bab","parentId":"253d3c70","timestamp":"2026-06-14T08:53:00.969Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来复盘 v7.04 的修改过程，并更新记忆。\n\n---\n\n## v7.04 复盘\n\n### 修改内容\n\n| 问题 | 原因 | 修复 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 降噪显示 0 时显示\"--\" | 有两处 noisereduce 调用，第二处使用错误的逻辑 `0显示\"—\"` | 删除第二处错误代码，保留正确逻辑 |\n| 手动模式下快门设置不生效 | 快门端点 `/Shutter` 只接受特定值，大部分值返回 400 | 改用 Exposure 端点设置 `<ShutterLevel>` |\n| 提示框未居中 | 使用普通定位 | 改用 `position:fixed` + `transform:translate(-50%,-50%)` |\n| 增益控制 | 未实现 | 添加 Gain 端点 API + 前端滑块 |\n\n### 关键发现\n\n1. **海康 ISAPI 手动曝光设置规则**：\n   - 快门：必须通过 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/exposure` 设置 `<ShutterLevel>`\n   - 光圈：可通过 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Iris` 独立设置\n   - 增益：可通过 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Gain` 独立设置\n\n2. **快门端点限制**：`/Shutter` 端点只接受特定值（如 1/25, 1/250, 1/1000），其他值返回 400 错误\n\n### 犯的错误\n\n1. **多次编辑导致文件损坏**：使用 edit 工具时没有提供足够的上下文，导致残留代码和重复代码\n   - 解决：从备份恢复后使用 Python 脚本精确定位删除\n\n---\n\n现在更新记忆："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b62cbd866fd744c88e641bc1","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"v7.04 降噪 快门 ISAPI 手动曝光"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":89460,"output":421,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89881,"cost":{"input":0.08946,"output":0.0013472000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0908072}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781427156070,"responseId":"cht000dd472@dx19ec5555fa0b9ca102"}}
{"type":"message","id":"25665b27","parentId":"deda6bab","timestamp":"2026-06-14T08:53:01.094Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b62cbd866fd744c88e641bc1","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [],\n  \"provider\": \"bedrock\",\n  \"model\": \"amazon.titan-embed-text-v2:0\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"debug\": {\n    \"backend\": \"builtin\",\n    \"effectiveMode\": \"n/a\",\n    \"searchMs\": 110,\n    \"hits\": 0\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"results":[],"provider":"bedrock","model":"amazon.titan-embed-text-v2:0","citations":"auto","debug":{"backend":"builtin","effectiveMode":"n/a","searchMs":110,"hits":0}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781427181094}}
{"type":"message","id":"87318b58","parentId":"25665b27","timestamp":"2026-06-14T08:53:26.306Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_07a84445a33c4a82a0f21469","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# v7.04 修复记录\n\n## 日期\n2026-06-14\n\n## 修复内容\n\n### 1. 降噪显示修复\n- **问题**：降噪设置为 0 时，PTZ 控制下的实时信息显示\"--\"\n- **原因**：`startPtzImagePoll` 函数中有两处 noisereduce 调用，第二处使用错误逻辑 `(nr.temporal_level === 0) ? '—' : ...`\n- **修复**：删除第二处错误代码，保留正确逻辑 `(nr.temporal_level !== undefined) ? nr.temporal_level : '--'`\n\n### 2. 手动曝光设置\n- **问题**：手动模式下设置快门/光圈，画面无变化\n- **关键发现**：海康 ISAPI 端点规则：\n  - 快门：**必须**通过 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/exposure` 设置 `<ShutterLevel>`\n  - 光圈：可通过 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Iris` 独立设置\n  - 增益：可通过 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Gain` 独立设置\n- **原因**：`/Shutter` 端点只接受特定值（1/25, 1/250, 1/1000），其他值返回 400\n- **修复**：router.py 中快门设置改用 Exposure 端点\n\n### 3. 提示框居中\n- **问题**：\"请连接设备\"提示框位置不在页面中央\n- **修复**：使用 `position:fixed; top:50%; left:50%; transform:translate(-50%, -50%)`\n\n### 4. 增益控制\n- **新增**：手动模式下增益滑块控制\n- **API**：`GET/POST /api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/image/gain`\n- **ISAPI**：`/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Gain`，字段 `<GainLevel>`\n\n## 犯的错误\n\n### edit 工具导致文件损坏\n- **现象**：多次使用 edit 工具修改同一文件，导致残留代码和重复代码\n- **原因**：oldText 匹配不够精确，或替换后产生重复内容\n- **教训**：\n  1. 编辑前先备份\n  2. 使用足够长的 oldText 确保唯一匹配\n  3. 如果发现重复代码，立即从备份恢复\n  4. 复杂修改使用 Python 脚本处理\n\n## 文件修改清单\n- `src/main/constants.py` - 版本号 v7.04\n- `src/api/router.py` - 快门设置改用 Exposure 端点，新增 Gain API\n- `src/web/includes/console.html` - 降噪显示修复，增益控制，提示框居中\n- `src/web/index.html` - 版本号 v7.04\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\.learnings\\v704_fixes.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":89989,"output":677,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90666,"cost":{"input":0.089989,"output":0.0021664,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0921554}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781427181097,"responseId":"cht000de507@dx19ec555b50cb85f582"}}
