{"type":"message","id":"b08c21aa","parentId":"f6b401c2","timestamp":"2026-06-14T08:53:57.961Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_952ce2290f204a7eb9cb9dc1","toolName":"memory_get","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"text\": \"# AstroHub 开发关键规则\\n\\n## ISAPI 接口规则\\n\\n### 1. XML 格式必须与 GET 响应一致\\n- GET 响应就是 PUT 应用的正确格式模板\\n- 大小写敏感：`manual`/`auto`（小写），不是 `Manual`/`Auto`\\n- 完整结构：降噪需要 `<mode>general</mode><GeneralMode><generalLevel>`\\n\\n### 2. 白平衡端点\\n- GET: `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance`\\n- 返回字段：`WhiteBalanceStyle`, `WhiteBalanceRed`, `WhiteBalanceBlue`\\n- PUT 格式必须与 GET 一致\\n\\n### 3. 降噪端点\\n- GET: `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/noiseReduce`\\n- 返回字段：`mode`, `GeneralMode/generalLevel`\\n- PUT 需要完整 `<mode>general</mode><GeneralMode>` 结构\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 测试验证标准\\n\\n### 连续5次测试\\n- 每次设置不同值\\n- 每次等待1秒\\n- ISAPI PUT 返回 200\\n- GET 验证值正确\",\n  \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\",\n  \"from\": 1,\n  \"lines\": 28\n}"}],"details":{"text":"# AstroHub 开发关键规则\n\n## ISAPI 接口规则\n\n### 1. XML 格式必须与 GET 响应一致\n- GET 响应就是 PUT 应用的正确格式模板\n- 大小写敏感：`manual`/`auto`（小写），不是 `Manual`/`Auto`\n- 完整结构：降噪需要 `<mode>general</mode><GeneralMode><generalLevel>`\n\n### 2. 白平衡端点\n- GET: `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance`\n- 返回字段：`WhiteBalanceStyle`, `WhiteBalanceRed`, `WhiteBalanceBlue`\n- PUT 格式必须与 GET 一致\n\n### 3. 降噪端点\n- GET: `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/noiseReduce`\n- 返回字段：`mode`, `GeneralMode/generalLevel`\n- PUT 需要完整 `<mode>general</mode><GeneralMode>` 结构\n\n---\n\n## 测试验证标准\n\n### 连续5次测试\n- 每次设置不同值\n- 每次等待1秒\n- ISAPI PUT 返回 200\n- GET 验证值正确","path":"MEMORY.md","from":1,"lines":28},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781427237961}}
{"type":"message","id":"ebf309e3","parentId":"b08c21aa","timestamp":"2026-06-14T08:54:27.418Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"更新 MEMORY.md，添加手动曝光端点规则："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-3a0128b3c9f046a2ba2fafab2dddb904","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"# AstroHub 开发关键规则\n\n## ISAPI 接口规则\n\n### 1. XML 格式必须与 GET 响应一致\n- GET 响应就是 PUT 应用的正确格式模板\n- 大小写敏感：`manual`/`auto`（小写），不是 `Manual`/`Auto`\n- 完整结构：降噪需要 `<mode>general</mode><GeneralMode><generalLevel>`\n\n### 2. 白平衡端点\n- GET: `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance`\n- 返回字段：`WhiteBalanceStyle`, `WhiteBalanceRed`, `WhiteBalanceBlue`\n- PUT 格式必须与 GET 一致\n\n### 3. 降噪端点\n- GET: `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/noiseReduce`\n- 返回字段：`mode`, `GeneralMode/generalLevel`\n- PUT 需要完整 `<mode>general</mode><GeneralMode>` 结构\n\n### 4. 手动曝光端点（v7.04 新增）\n- **快门**：必须通过 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/exposure` 设置 `<ShutterLevel>`\n  - `/Shutter` 端点只接受特定值（1/25, 1/250, 1/1000），其他返回 400\n- **光圈**：可通过 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Iris` 独立设置 `<IrisLevel>`\n- **增益**：可通过 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Gain` 独立设置 `<GainLevel>`\n- **曝光模式**：`/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/exposure`，字段 `<ExposureType>`（不是 ExposureMode）\n\n---\n\n## 测试验证标准","oldText":"# AstroHub 开发关键规则\n\n## ISAPI 接口规则\n\n### 1. XML 格式必须与 GET 响应一致"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":86877,"output":483,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87360,"cost":{"input":0.086877,"output":0.0015456,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.08842259999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781427237964,"responseId":"cht000ddb79@dx19ec5568b42b894142"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7fda5e05","parentId":"ebf309e3","timestamp":"2026-06-14T08:54:27.441Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-3a0128b3c9f046a2ba2fafab2dddb904","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find the exact text in C:\\\\Users\\\\admin\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\dev-factory\\\\astrohub\\\\MEMORY.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\\nCurrent file contents:\\n# MEMORY.md\\n\\n## 海康 ISAPI 关键发现\\n\\n### Focus 控制端点（重要）\\n- **正确端点**: `PUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus`\\n- **请求格式**:\\n  ```xml\\n  <?xml version=\\\"1.0\\\" encoding=\\\"UTF-8\\\"?>\\n  <FocusData>\\n    <focus>60</focus>   <!-- 正数=后移/远焦，负数=前移/近焦 -->\\n  </FocusData>\\n  ```\\n- **停止**: `<focus>0</focus>`\\n- **固定值**: 官方界面使用固定值 60，不是可调参数\\n\\n### PTZ 控制端点\\n- **Continuous**: `PUT /ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/continuous`\\n- **速度范围**: pan/tilt/zoom 都是 -10 到 10（ISAPI 2.0 规范）\\n- **注意**: 设备 capabilities 可能不显示 ContinuousFocusSpace，但 Focus 需用单独端点\\n\\n### OSD 控制端点\\n- **PTZ OSD**: `PUT /ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/PTZOSDDisplay` (~300ms)\\n- **OSD Info**: `PUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/overlays` (~2-4秒，设备固有延迟)\\n- **ns0: 命名空间**: `ET.tostring` 会产生 `ns0:` 前缀，海康拒绝，需字符串替换移除\\n\\n## 海康摄像头型号\\n- **型号**: iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A\\n- **Zoom 范围**: 10-\\n... (truncated)\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"edit","error":"Could not find the exact text in C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\MEMORY.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\nCurrent file contents:\n# MEMORY.md\n\n## 海康 ISAPI 关键发现\n\n### Focus 控制端点（重要）\n- **正确端点**: `PUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus`\n- **请求格式**:\n  ```xml\n  <?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n  <FocusData>\n    <focus>60</focus>   <!-- 正数=后移/远焦，负数=前移/近焦 -->\n  </FocusData>\n  ```\n- **停止**: `<focus>0</focus>`\n- **固定值**: 官方界面使用固定值 60，不是可调参数\n\n### PTZ 控制端点\n- **Continuous**: `PUT /ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/continuous`\n- **速度范围**: pan/tilt/zoom 都是 -10 到 10（ISAPI 2.0 规范）\n- **注意**: 设备 capabilities 可能不显示 ContinuousFocusSpace，但 Focus 需用单独端点\n\n### OSD 控制端点\n- **PTZ OSD**: `PUT /ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/PTZOSDDisplay` (~300ms)\n- **OSD Info**: `PUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/overlays` (~2-4秒，设备固有延迟)\n- **ns0: 命名空间**: `ET.tostring` 会产生 `ns0:` 前缀，海康拒绝，需字符串替换移除\n\n## 海康摄像头型号\n- **型号**: iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A\n- **Zoom 范围**: 10-\n... (truncated)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781427267441}}
{"type":"message","id":"b916680c","parentId":"7fda5e05","timestamp":"2026-06-14T08:54:41.747Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"文件内容不同。让我读取完整文件："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_86538ecac70e415a959e00fc","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":1,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":92870,"output":51,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92921,"cost":{"input":0.09287,"output":0.0001632,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0930332}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781427267443,"responseId":"cht000ddced@dx19ec557074bb85e102"}}
{"type":"message","id":"47578154","parentId":"b916680c","timestamp":"2026-06-14T08:54:41.753Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_86538ecac70e415a959e00fc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md\n\n## 海康 ISAPI 关键发现\n\n### Focus 控制端点（重要）\n- **正确端点**: `PUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus`\n- **请求格式**:\n  ```xml\n  <?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n  <FocusData>\n    <focus>60</focus>   <!-- 正数=后移/远焦，负数=前移/近焦 -->\n  </FocusData>\n  ```\n- **停止**: `<focus>0</focus>`\n- **固定值**: 官方界面使用固定值 60，不是可调参数\n\n### PTZ 控制端点\n- **Continuous**: `PUT /ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/continuous`\n- **速度范围**: pan/tilt/zoom 都是 -10 到 10（ISAPI 2.0 规范）\n- **注意**: 设备 capabilities 可能不显示 ContinuousFocusSpace，但 Focus 需用单独端点\n\n### OSD 控制端点\n- **PTZ OSD**: `PUT /ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/PTZOSDDisplay` (~300ms)\n- **OSD Info**: `PUT /ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/overlays` (~2-4秒，设备固有延迟)\n- **ns0: 命名空间**: `ET.tostring` 会产生 `ns0:` 前缀，海康拒绝，需字符串替换移除\n\n## 海康摄像头型号\n- **型号**: iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A\n- **Zoom 范围**: 10-320\n- **Pan/Tilt 范围**: 0-3600 / -200-900\n- **认证**: Digest Auth\n\n## Playwright 捕获官方请求方法\n1. 登录后进入预览页面\n2. 聚焦按钮在预览页面右侧，title=\"聚焦 +\" / title=\"聚焦 -\"\n3. 使用 `page.on('request', ...)` 捕获 ISAPI 请求\n4. 官方界面是动态加载的 Vue 应用，需等待足够时间\n\n## 常见错误\n\n### 速度缩放问题\n- **错误**: 在 `ptz_move` 和 `continuous_move` 两层都做缩放\n- **修复**: 只在 `continuous_move` 做一次缩放，或直接传原始值\n\n### Focus 端点错误\n- **错误**: 使用 PTZ continuous 的 `<focus>` 参数（设备不支持）\n- **修复**: 使用单独的 `/System/Video/inputs/channels/1/focus` 端点\n\n### 前端按钮事件\n- **错误**: 只用 `onmousedown` 没有处理 `mouseup`\n- **修复**: 添加 `onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\"` 或使用全局 mouseup 监听\n\n## 项目配置\n- **AstroHub 端口**: 10280\n- **设备 IP**: 192.168.5.72\n- **认证**: admin / Nftw1357\n\n## WASM SDK 配置（重要）\n- **szBasePath**: `/static/websdk/wasm`\n- **SDK 内部路径拼接**: `szBasePath + \"/playctrl/PlayCtrlWasm/...\"`\n- **Playwright 限制**: `importScripts` 错误是 Chromium 安全限制，真实浏览器正常\n- **版本**: v6.54（2026-06-14）\n\n## 连接状态管理（重要）\n\n### 字段定义\n- **active_device**: 当前活跃设备 MAC，用于所有功能复用（PTZ操作、画面控制等）\n- **last_connected**: 上次连接的设备 MAC，用于快速连接、断开后重连\n- **_controllers**: PTZManager 字典，存储真实的连接状态（key: IP, value: PTZController）\n\n### 操作流程\n1. 连接成功: 更新 `active_device` + `last_connected` + `_controllers[ip]`\n2. 断开连接: 清空 `active_device`，保留 `last_connected`，删除 `_controllers[ip]`\n3. 功能复用: 检查 `_controllers`，如果不存在则尝试自动重连\n4. 快速连接: 读取 `last_connected` 获取设备信息和凭据\n\n### 前端操作锁\n- `_connectionOperationInProgress`: 防止重复点击\n- 连接成功后等待3秒才启用按钮（等待视频播放）\n- 断开后禁用所有控件，显示\"请先连接设备\"\n\n[1 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781427281753}}
{"type":"message","id":"d37f96a0","parentId":"47578154","timestamp":"2026-06-14T08:55:02.136Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"添加手动曝光规则到 MEMORY.md："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-a4237c4d97574dbebe17d1ec3189c216","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"## WASM SDK 配置（重要）\n- **szBasePath**: `/static/websdk/wasm`\n- **SDK 内部路径拼接**: `szBasePath + \"/playctrl/PlayCtrlWasm/...\"`\n- **Playwright 限制**: `importScripts` 错误是 Chromium 安全限制，真实浏览器正常\n- **版本**: v7.04（2026-06-14）\n\n## 手动曝光控制（v7.04 新增）\n\n### 端点规则\n- **快门**: 必须通过 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/exposure` 设置 `<ShutterLevel>`\n  - `/Shutter` 端点只接受特定值（1/25, 1/250, 1/1000），其他返回 400\n- **光圈**: 可通过 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Iris` 独立设置 `<IrisLevel>`\n- **增益**: 可通过 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Gain` 独立设置 `<GainLevel>`\n- **曝光模式**: 字段名 `<ExposureType>`（不是 ExposureMode）\n\n### 测试验证\n```bash\n# 设置手动模式 + 快门\ncurl -X PUT http://192.168.5.72/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/exposure\n  -d '<Exposure><ExposureType>manual</ExposureType><ShutterLevel>1/250</ShutterLevel></Exposure>'\n\n# 设置增益\ncurl -X PUT http://192.168.5.72/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Gain\n  -d '<Gain><GainLevel>50</GainLevel></Gain>'\n```","oldText":"## WASM SDK 配置（重要）\n- **szBasePath**: `/static/websdk/wasm`\n- **SDK 内部路径拼接**: `szBasePath + \"/playctrl/PlayCtrlWasm/...\"`\n- **Playwright 限制**: `importScripts` 错误是 Chromium 安全限制，真实浏览器正常\n- **版本**: v6.54（2026-06-14）"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":88900,"output":531,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89431,"cost":{"input":0.08889999999999999,"output":0.0016992,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.09059919999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781427281755,"responseId":"cht000d523d@dx19ec5573452b87f702"}}
