{"type":"message","id":"339d3816","parentId":"289a333c","timestamp":"2026-06-14T09:08:49.962Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**关键发现**：\n\n快门设置成功！通过 Exposure 端点设置 `<ShutterLevel>` 是正确的。\n\n问题可能是：\n1. 前端设置后没有等待足够时间让画面变化\n2. 或者 router.py 的实现有问题\n\n让我检查 router.py 的快门设置实现："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-67e7d9a6134b433e973f9d485af3a87f","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":3018,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":98748,"output":108,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98856,"cost":{"input":0.098748,"output":0.00034560000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0990936}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781428120889,"responseId":"cht000d83a7@dx19ec563f2beb9cb212"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0617f054","parentId":"339d3816","timestamp":"2026-06-14T09:08:49.969Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-67e7d9a6134b433e973f9d485af3a87f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@api_router.post(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/shutter\", summary=\"设置快门\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def set_shutter(device_id: str, data: dict) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"设置快门参数 - v7.04: 使用 Exposure 端点设置 ShutterLevel\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        level = data.get(\"level\", \"1/60\")\r\n        \r\n        # v7.04: 快门必须通过 Exposure 端点设置\r\n        xml_str = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<Exposure version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n  <ExposureType>manual</ExposureType>\r\n  <ShutterLevel>{level}</ShutterLevel>\r\n</Exposure>'''\r\n\r\n        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/exposure\", xml_str)\r\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": f\"快门已设置为 {level}\"}\r\n\n[361 more lines in file. Use offset=3048 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781428129969}}
{"type":"message","id":"d922496f","parentId":"0617f054","timestamp":"2026-06-14T09:09:31.719Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"发现问题！**快门设置时总是把曝光模式设置为 manual**！\n\n这会导致：\n1. 如果用户想保持自动模式，但只调整快门上限，会被强制改成手动模式\n2. 如果已经是手动模式，再次设置会覆盖其他设置（如光圈、增益）\n\n**正确做法**：应该先获取当前曝光模式，然后在设置快门时保持当前模式。\n\n让我修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-f448032dbdfd42cf927264f81d8f10a0","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"@api_router.post(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/shutter\", summary=\"设置快门\", tags=[\"Image\"])\nasync def set_shutter(device_id: str, data: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"设置快门参数 - v7.06: 保持当前曝光模式\"\"\"\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")\n    if not mgr:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\n\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\n    if not target_ip:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\n\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\n    if err:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\n\n    client = ctrl.client\n    try:\n        level = data.get(\"level\", \"1/60\")\n        \n        # v7.06: 先获取当前曝光模式\n        get_resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/exposure\")\n        current_mode = \"manual\"\n        if get_resp.status_code == 200:\n            root = ET.fromstring(get_resp.xml)\n            for elem in root.iter():\n                tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\n                if tag in (\"ExposureType\", \"exposureType\"):\n                    current_mode = elem.text or \"manual\"\n        \n        # v7.06: 保持当前曝光模式\n        xml_str = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<Exposure version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n  <ExposureType>{current_mode}</ExposureType>\n  <ShutterLevel>{level}</ShutterLevel>\n</Exposure>'''\n\n        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/exposure\", xml_str)\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": f\"快门已设置为 {level}\"}","oldText":"@api_router.post(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/shutter\", summary=\"设置快门\", tags=[\"Image\"])\nasync def set_shutter(device_id: str, data: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"设置快门参数 - v7.04: 使用 Exposure 端点设置 ShutterLevel\"\"\"\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")\n    if not mgr:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\n\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\n    if not target_ip:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\n\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\n    if err:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\n\n    client = ctrl.client\n    try:\n        level = data.get(\"level\", \"1/60\")\n        \n        # v7.04: 快门必须通过 Exposure 端点设置\n        xml_str = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<Exposure version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n  <ExposureType>manual</ExposureType>\n  <ShutterLevel>{level}</ShutterLevel>\n</Exposure>''\n\n        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/exposure\", xml_str)\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": f\"快门已设置为 {level}\"}"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":99228,"output":1032,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100260,"cost":{"input":0.099228,"output":0.0033024000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1025304}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781428129971,"responseId":"cht000deea7@dx19ec5641ffbba60352"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a590e2de","parentId":"d922496f","timestamp":"2026-06-14T09:09:31.738Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-f448032dbdfd42cf927264f81d8f10a0","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find the exact text in C:\\\\Users\\\\admin\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\dev-factory\\\\astrohub\\\\src\\\\api\\\\router.py. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\\nCurrent file contents:\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\r\\nAstroHub v2.0 - 统一路由聚合\\r\\n\\r\\n整合 M1-M11 所有模块路由到 /api/v1/ 下:\\r\\n- /api/v1/health            - 全局健康检查\\r\\n- /api/v1/discovery/sadp    - SADP 设备发现\\r\\n- /api/v1/devices/*         - 设备管理（真实）\\r\\n- /api/v1/ptz/*             - PTZ 控制（真实）\\r\\n- /api/v1/streams/*         - 流服务\\r\\n- /api/v1/calibration/*     - 校准\\r\\n- /api/v1/ascom/*           - ASCOM 设备\\r\\n- /api/v1/settings          - 系统设置\\r\\n\\r\\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\\r\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\nfrom __future__ import annotations\\r\\n\\r\\nimport time\\r\\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\\r\\nfrom typing import Any\\r\\n\\r\\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\\r\\nfrom fastapi import APIRouter, FastAPI, Query\\r\\nfrom fastapi.responses import JSONResponse\\r\\n\\r\\n# v6.40: 操作日志\\r\\nfrom src.operation_logger import log_api, log_web, log_error, log_info\\r\\n\\r\\n# ================================================================ #\\r\\n#  \\n... (truncated)\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"edit","error":"Could not find the exact text in C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\nCurrent file contents:\n\"\"\"\r\nAstroHub v2.0 - 统一路由聚合\r\n\r\n整合 M1-M11 所有模块路由到 /api/v1/ 下:\r\n- /api/v1/health            - 全局健康检查\r\n- /api/v1/discovery/sadp    - SADP 设备发现\r\n- /api/v1/devices/*         - 设备管理（真实）\r\n- /api/v1/ptz/*             - PTZ 控制（真实）\r\n- /api/v1/streams/*         - 流服务\r\n- /api/v1/calibration/*     - 校准\r\n- /api/v1/ascom/*           - ASCOM 设备\r\n- /api/v1/settings          - 系统设置\r\n\r\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\r\n\"\"\"\r\n\r\nfrom __future__ import annotations\r\n\r\nimport time\r\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\r\nfrom typing import Any\r\n\r\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\r\nfrom fastapi import APIRouter, FastAPI, Query\r\nfrom fastapi.responses import JSONResponse\r\n\r\n# v6.40: 操作日志\r\nfrom src.operation_logger import log_api, log_web, log_error, log_info\r\n\r\n# ================================================================ #\r\n#  \n... (truncated)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781428171737}}
