{"type":"message","id":"9237d81e","parentId":"3fa7c27e","timestamp":"2026-06-14T09:12:53.843Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**E2E 测试全部通过！**\n\n---\n\n## v7.06 修复总结\n\n### 修复内容\n\n| 问题 | 原因 | 修复 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 降噪设置不生效 | ISAPI 字段名错误（spatialLevel 应为 FrameNoiseReduceLevel） | 代码已使用正确字段名，API 正常工作 |\n| 手动模式下快门设置不生效 | 设置快门时强制改为 manual 模式，覆盖了当前曝光状态 | 修改为先获取当前曝光模式，保持当前模式 |\n\n### 测试结果\n\n```\n[PASS] Version v7.06\n[PASS] DNR Spatial Exists\n[PASS] DNR Temporal Exists  \n[PASS] Auto Mode Set\n[PASS] Shutter Enabled in Manual\n[PASS] Iris Enabled in Manual\n[PASS] Gain Enabled in Manual\n[PASS] Shutter Set to 1/1000\n```\n\n### 修改文件\n\n- `src/main/constants.py` - 版本号 v7.06\n- `src/api/router.py` - 修复 set_shutter 函数，保持当前曝光模式\n- `src/web/index.html` - 版本号 v7.06"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":115246,"output":258,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115504,"cost":{"input":0.115246,"output":0.0008256000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1160716}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781428361057,"responseId":"cht000d6df7@dx19ec567a524b958232"}}
