{"type":"message","id":"5bce04f2","parentId":"dd7f5fac","timestamp":"2026-06-14T09:54:29.257Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**关键发现**：\n\n1. **Exposure 端点不保存 ShutterLevel** - 设置后 Exposure 响应中没有 ShutterLevel 字段\n2. **Exposure 端点只接受 ExposureType** - ShutterLevel 被忽略了\n\n这说明海康设备的 ISAPI 逻辑是：\n- **曝光模式**：通过 `/exposure` 端点设置 `<ExposureType>`\n- **快门**：通过独立的 `/Shutter` 端点设置 `<ShutterLevel>`\n- **光圈**：通过独立的 `/Iris` 端点设置 `<IrisLevel>`\n\n但 `/Shutter` 端点只接受特定值（1/25, 1/250, 1/1000）。这意味着：\n1. 要么设备固件限制了快门值的范围\n2. 要么需要其他方式设置快门\n\n让我查看海康官方文档中的快门设置方式。先测试一下是否需要在 Exposure 中同时传递其他字段："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_58023cf28ba747fabf2ae696","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n测试通过 Exposure 端点设置快门 - 完整字段版\n\"\"\"\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\nimport time\n\nBASE_URL = \"http://192.168.5.72\"\nAUTH = HTTPDigestAuth('admin', 'Nftw1357')\n\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\nprint(\"测试完整字段版\")\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\n\n# 1. 设置手动模式\nprint(\"\\n1. 设置手动模式\")\nxml_str = '''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<Exposure version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n  <ExposureType>manual</ExposureType>\n</Exposure>'''\nresp = requests.put(f'{BASE_URL}/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/exposure', \n                   auth=AUTH, data=xml_str,\n                   headers={'Content-Type': 'application/xml'}, timeout=5)\nprint(f'状态: {resp.status_code}')\n\n# 2. 尝试设置快门 - 使用 ShutterPriority 模式\nprint(\"\\n2. 使用 ShutterPriority 模式\")\nxml_str = '''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<Exposure version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n  <ExposureType>shutter-priority</ExposureType>\n  <ShutterLevel>1/250</ShutterLevel>\n</Exposure>'''\nresp = requests.put(f'{BASE_URL}/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/exposure', \n                   auth=AUTH, data=xml_str,\n                   headers={'Content-Type': 'application/xml'}, timeout=5)\nprint(f'状态: {resp.status_code}')\nprint(f'响应: {resp.text}')\n\ntime.sleep(1)\n\n# 3. 验证快门\nresp = requests.get(f'{BASE_URL}/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Shutter', auth=AUTH, timeout=5)\nprint(f'快门: {resp.text}')\n\n# 4. 恢复手动模式\nprint(\"\\n4. 恢复手动模式\")\nxml_str = '''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<Exposure version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n  <ExposureType>manual</ExposureType>\n</Exposure>'''\nresp = requests.put(f'{BASE_URL}/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/exposure', \n                   auth=AUTH, data=xml_str,\n                   headers={'Content-Type': 'application/xml'}, timeout=5)\nprint(f'状态: {resp.status_code}')\n\n# 5. 通过 Shutter 端点设置（使用可接受的值）\nprint(\"\\n5. 通过 Shutter 端点设置 1/250\")\nxml_str = '''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<Shutter version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n  <ShutterLevel>1/250</ShutterLevel>\n</Shutter>'''\nresp = requests.put(f'{BASE_URL}/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Shutter', \n                   auth=AUTH, data=xml_str,\n                   headers={'Content-Type': 'application/xml'}, timeout=5)\nprint(f'状态: {resp.status_code}')\n\ntime.sleep(1)\n\n# 6. 验证快门\nresp = requests.get(f'{BASE_URL}/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Shutter', auth=AUTH, timeout=5)\nprint(f'快门: {resp.text}')\n\n# 7. 恢复自动模式\nprint(\"\\n7. 恢复自动模式\")\nxml_str = '''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<Exposure version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n  <ExposureType>auto</ExposureType>\n</Exposure>'''\nresp = requests.put(f'{BASE_URL}/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/exposure', \n                   auth=AUTH, data=xml_str,\n                   headers={'Content-Type': 'application/xml'}, timeout=5)\nprint(f'状态: {resp.status_code}')","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\test_shutter_complete.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":123171,"output":1159,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124330,"cost":{"input":0.12317099999999999,"output":0.0037088000