{"type":"message","id":"ed32e86a","parentId":"ec223fa5","timestamp":"2026-06-14T10:46:09.016Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"关键函数是 `traverse_function`（第 629 行）。我需要：\n\n1. 添加从 capabilities 端点读取 opt 值的逻辑\n2. 将 opt 值存入 function.json\n\n让我查看 `_parse_range` 函数："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_baba8302920b4fdd838f41a2","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":434,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\function.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":145918,"output":102,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146020,"cost":{"input":0.145918,"output":0.0003264,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1462444}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781433961644,"responseId":"cht000d4e5c@dx19ec5bd0e37b91a742"}}
{"type":"message","id":"802b5ebb","parentId":"ed32e86a","timestamp":"2026-06-14T10:46:09.024Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_baba8302920b4fdd838f41a2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def _parse_range(self, root: ET.Element, key: str) -> tuple[str | int, str | int]:\n        \"\"\"从 XML 响应中解析指定 key 的取值范围。\"\"\"\n        min_val = 0\n        max_val = 100\n        for elem in root.iter():\n            local_name = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1].lower() if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag.lower()\n            if \"min\" in local_name and key.lower() in local_name and elem.text:\n                try:\n                    min_val = int(elem.text.strip())\n                except (ValueError, TypeError):\n                    min_val = elem.text.strip()\n            if \"max\" in local_name and key.lower() in local_name and elem.text:\n                try:\n                    max_val = int(elem.text.strip())\n                except (ValueError, TypeError):\n                    max_val = elem.text.strip()\n            # Hikvision range=\"0,100\" 格式\n            if \"range\" in local_name and elem.text:\n                try:\n                    if \"[\" in elem.text:\n                        parts = elem.text.strip().split(\"[\")[1].split(\"]\")[0].split(\",\")\n                        if len(parts) == 2:\n                            min_val = int(parts[0].strip())\n                            max_val = int(parts[1].strip())\n                    elif \",\" in elem.text:\n                        parts = elem.text.strip().split(\",\")\n                        if len(parts) == 2:\n                            min_val = int(parts[0].strip())\n                            max_val = int(parts[1].strip())\n                except (IndexError, ValueError):\n                    pass\n        return min_val, max_val\n\n    def _probe_endpoint(self, endpoint: str) -> ISAPIResponse:\n        \"\"\"探测 ISAPI 端点是否存在。\"\"\"\n        return self.client.get(endpoint)\n\n    def _build_xml_from_template(self, original_xml: str, cap_def: dict, value: Any) -> str:\n        \"\"\"基于原始 XML 模板,修改指定字段后返回新 XML。\n\n\n[750 more lines in file. Use offset=474 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781433969024}}
{"type":"message","id":"a5906ad1","parentId":"802b5ebb","timestamp":"2026-06-14T10:46:18.044Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我需要添加一个新方法 `_parse_opt_values` 来从 capabilities 端点获取 `opt` 值列表。\n\n让我添加这个功能。先查看 capabilities 端点的 XML 格式：\n\n```xml\n<Shutter>\n  <ShutterLevel opt=\"1/25,1/50,1/75,1/100,...\">1/1000</ShutterLevel>\n</Shutter>\n\n<Iris>\n  <IrisLevel opt=\"160,200,240,...\">280</IrisLevel>\n</Iris>\n```\n\n添加解析 opt 值的方法："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-b0c23d034e234dfcbd68e93e6fe6055b","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":462,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\function.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":136801,"output":169,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136970,"cost":{"input":0.136801,"output":0.0005408,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1373418}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781433969028,"responseId":"cht000d4f8c@dx19ec5bd2af8b91a742"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b230df57","parentId":"a5906ad1","timestamp":"2026-06-14T10:46:18.054Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-b0c23d034e234dfcbd68e93e6fe6055b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                            max_val = int(parts[1].strip())\n                except (IndexError, ValueError):\n                    pass\n        return min_val, max_val\n\n    def _probe_endpoint(self, endpoint: str) -> ISAPIResponse:\n        \"\"\"探测 ISAPI 端点是否存在。\"\"\"\n        return self.client.get(endpoint)\n\n    def _build_xml_from_template(self, original_xml: str, cap_def: dict, value: Any) -> str:\n        \"\"\"基于原始 XML 模板,修改指定字段后返回新 XML。\n\n        重要:海康设备不接受带命名空间前缀的XML(如 ns0:),\n        所以必须使用正则替换而非 ET.tostring()。\n        \"\"\"\n        import re\n\n        key = cap_def.get(\"test_key\", \"\")\n\n        # 单字段模式:用正则替换值\n        if \"test_keys\" not in cap_def:\n            # 匹配 <key>原值</key>\n            pattern = rf\"(<{key}>)[^<]*(</{key}>)\"\n            if re.search(pattern, original_xml, re.IGNORECASE):\n                new_xml = re.sub(pattern, rf\"\\g<1>{value}\\g<2>\", original_xml, flags=re.IGNORECASE)\n                return new_xml\n            # 尝试带命名空间的匹配:<ns:key>原值</ns:key>\n            pattern_ns = rf\"(<[\\w]+:{key}>)[^<]*(</[\\w]+:{key}>)\"\n            if re.search(pattern_ns, original_xml, re.IGNORECASE):\n                new_xml = re.sub(pattern_ns, rf\"\\g<1>{value}\\g<2>\", original_xml, flags=re.IGNORECASE)\n\n[732 more lines in file. Use offset=492 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781433978054}}
{"type":"message","id":"95207e3a","parentId":"b230df57","timestamp":"2026-06-14T10:47:04.948Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我需要在 `_parse_range` 后添加一个 `_parse_opt_values` 方法，然后修改 `traverse_function` 来调用 capabilities 端点并存储 opt 值。\n\n这需要较大的修改。让我创建一个精确的修改脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1bfe615f8cb5456a9d1a9a47","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n修改 function.py - 添加从 capabilities 获取 opt 值的功能\n\"\"\"\n\n# 读取文件\nwith open('src/advanced/function.py', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# 1. 在 _parse_range 后添加 _parse_opt_values 方法\nnew_method = '''\n\n    def _parse_opt_values(self, root: ET.Element, key: str) -> list[str] | None:\n        \"\"\"v7.08: 从 XML 响应中解析指定 key 的 opt 属性值列表。\n        \n        用于解析 capabilities 端点返回的可选值列表，如:\n        <ShutterLevel opt=\"1/25,1/50,1/75,...\">1/1000</ShutterLevel>\n        \n        Returns:\n            opt 值列表，如 [\"1/25\", \"1/50\", \"1/75\", ...]，如果没有 opt 属性则返回 None\n        \"\"\"\n        for elem in root.iter():\n            local_name = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\n            if local_name.lower() == key.lower():\n                opt_attr = elem.get(\"opt\")\n                if opt_attr:\n                    # 解析逗号分隔的值\n                    values = [v.strip() for v in opt_attr.split(\",\")]\n                    return values\n        return None\n\n    def _fetch_capabilities_opt_values(self, endpoint_base: str, key: str) -> list[str] | None:\n        \"\"\"v7.08: 从 capabilities 端点获取 opt 值列表。\n        \n        Args:\n            endpoint_base: 基础端点，如 \"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\"\n            key: 字段名，如 \"ShutterLevel\"\n        \n        Returns:\n            opt 值列表\n        \"\"\"\n        # 构建 capabilities 端点\n        cap_endpoint = endpoint_base.rsplit(\"/\", 1)[0] + \"/capabilities\"\n        if \"/Image/channels/\" in endpoint_base:\n            # /Image/channels/1/Shutter -> /Image/channels/1/capabilities\n            cap_endpoint = \"/Image/channels/\" + str(self.channel) + \"/capabilities\"\n        \n        try:\n            resp = self._probe_endpoint(cap_endpoint)\n            if resp.status_code == 200:\n                root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n                return self._parse_opt_values(root, key)\n        except Exception as e:\n            pass\n        return None\n'''\n\n# 找到 _probe_endpoint 方法的位置并插入新方法\ninsert_after = '''    def _probe_endpoint(self, endpoint: str) -> ISAPIResponse:\n        \"\"\"探测 ISAPI 端点是否存在。\"\"\"\n        return self.client.get(endpoint)'''\n\ncontent = content.replace(insert_after, insert_after + new_method)\n\n# 2. 修改 traverse_function 中 shutter 模式的处理，添加 opt_values\n# 找到 shutter 模式的处理代码块\nold_shutter_block = '''            # v6.20: shutter mode - 快门需要特殊处理\n            if mode == \"shutter\":\n                root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n                val = self._parse_xml_value(root, cap_def[\"test_key\"])\n                result.current_values = {cap_def[\"test_key\"]: val}\n                \n                # 使用预定义范围或从 XML 解析\n                min_range, max_range = self._parse_range(root, cap_def[\"test_key\"])\n                if min_range == 0 and max_range == 100:\n                    min_range = cap_def.get(\"range_min\", \"1/30000\")\n                    max_range = cap_def.get(\"range_max\", \"1/25\")\n                \n                result.min_val = min_range\n                result.max_val = max_range\n                \n                # 测试一个快门值\n                test_val = cap_def.get(\"test_value\", \"1/100\")\n                success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, test_val, item_key)'''\n\nnew_shutter_block = '''            # v7.08: shutter mode - 从 capabilities 获取 opt 值列表\n            if mode == \"shutter\":\n                root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n                val = self._parse_xml_value(root, cap_def[\"test_key\"])\n                result.current_values = {cap_def[\"test_key\"]: val}\n                \n                # v7.08: 尝试从 capabilities 端点获取 opt 值列表\n                opt_values = self._fetch_capabilities_opt_values(endpoint, cap_def[\"test_key\"])\n                if opt_values:\n                    result.opt_values = opt_values\n                    result.min_val = opt_values[0] if opt_values else cap_def.get(\"range_min\", \"1/30000\")\n                    result.max_val = opt_values[-1] if opt_values else cap_def.get(\"range_max\", \"1/25\")\n                else:\n                    # 回退到预定义范围\n                    min_range, max_range = self._parse_range(root, cap_def[\"test_key\"])\n                    if min_range == 0 and max_range == 100:\n                        min_range = cap_def.get(\"range_min\", \"1/30000\")\n                        max_range = cap_def.get(\"range_max\", \"1/25\")\n                    result.min_val = min_range\n                    result.max_val = max_range\n                \n                # 测试一个快门值（使用 opt_values 中的值或预定义值）\n                if opt_values and len(opt_values) > 5:\n                    test_val = opt_values[5]  # 使用中间值测试\n                else:\n                    test_val = cap_def.get(\"test_value\", \"1/100\")\n                success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, test_val, item_key)'''\n\ncontent = content.replace(old_shutter_block, new_shutter_block)\n\n# 3. 修改 iris 模式的处理\nold_iris_block = '''            # v6.20: iris mode - 光圈使用离散值列表\n            if mode == \"iris\":\n                root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n                val = self._parse_xml_value(root, cap_def[\"test_key\"])\n                result.current_values = {cap_def[\"test_key\"]: val}\n                \n                result.min_val = cap_def.get(\"range_min\", 160)\n                result.max_val = cap_def.get(\"range_max\", 2200)\n                \n                # 测试一个光圈值\n                test_val = cap_def.get(\"test_value\", 160)\n                success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, test_val, item_key)'''\n\nnew_iris_block = '''            # v7.08: iris mode - 从 capabilities 获取 opt 值列表\n            if mode == \"iris\":\n                root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n                val = self._parse_xml_value(root, cap_def[\"test_key\"])\n                result.current_values = {cap_def[\"test_key\"]: val}\n                \n                # v7.08: 尝试从 capabilities 端点获取 opt 值列表\n                opt_values = self._fetch_capabilities_opt_values(endpoint, cap_def[\"test_key\"])\n                if opt_values:\n                    result.opt_values = opt_values\n                    result.min_val = opt_values[0] if opt_values else cap_def.get(\"range_min\", 160)\n                    result.max_val = opt_values[-1] if opt_values else cap_def.get(\"range_max\", 2200)\n                else:\n                    result.min_val = cap_def.get(\"range_min\", 160)\n                    result.max_val = cap_def.get(\"range_max\", 2200)\n                \n                # 测试一个光圈值\n                test_val = cap_def.get(\"test_value\", 160)\n                success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, test_val, item_key)'''\n\ncontent = content.replace(old_iris_block, new_iris_block)\n\n# 4. 修改 FunctionResult 数据类，添加 opt_values 字段\nold_dataclass = '''@dataclass\nclass FunctionResult:\n    \"\"\"单次功能探测结果。\"\"\"\n    p_id: str = \"\"\n    item: str = \"\"\n    label: str = \"\"\n    supported: bool = False\n    endpoint: str = \"\"\n    test_key: str = \"\"\n    min_val: str | int = 0\n    max_val: str | int = 100\n    current_values: dict[str, Any] = field(default_factory=dict)\n    test_results: list[dict] = field(default_factory=list)\n    restored: bool = False\n    error: str | None = None\n    config_entry: dict = field(default_factory=dict)'''\n\nnew_dataclass = '''@dataclass\nclass FunctionResult:\n    \"\"\"单次功能探测结果。\"\"\"\n    p_id: str = \"\"\n    item: str = \"\"\n    label: str = \"\"\n    supported: bool = False\n    endpoint: str = \"\"\n    test_key: str = \"\"\n    min_val: str | int = 0\n    max_val: str | int = 100\n    opt_values: list[str] | None = None  # v7.08: 可选值列表\n    current_values: dict[str, Any] = field(default_factory=dict)\n    test_results: list[dict] = field(default_factory=list)\n    restored: bool = False\n    error: str | None = None\n    config_entry: dict = field(default_factory=dict)'''\n\ncontent = content.replace(old_dataclass, new_dataclass)\n\n# 5. 修改 _write_config 方法，保存 opt_values\nold_write_config = '''        config[\"function_detection\"][result.p_id or result.item] = {\n            \"p_id\": result.p_id,\n            \"item\": result.item,\n            \"label\": result.label,\n            \"supported\": result.supported,\n            \"endpoint\": result.endpoint,\n            \"min_val\": result.min_val,\n            \"max_val\": result.max_val,\n            \"current_values\": result.current_values,\n            \"test_results\": result.test_results,\n            \"restored\": result.restored,\n            \"error\": result.error,\n        }'''\n\nnew_write_config = '''        entry = {\n            \"p_id\": result.p_id,\n            \"item\": result.item,\n            \"label\": result.label,\n            \"supported\": result.supported,\n            \"endpoint\": result.endpoint,\n            \"min_val\": result.min_val,\n            \"max_val\": result.max_val,\n            \"current_values\": result.current_values,\n            \"test_results\": result.test_results,\n            \"restored\": result.restored,\n            \"error\": result.error,\n        }\n        # v7.08: 保存 opt_values（如果有）\n        if result.opt_values:\n            entry[\"opt_values\"] = result.opt_values\n        config[\"function_detection\"][result.p_id or result.item] = entry'''\n\ncontent = content.replace(old_write_config, new_write_config)\n\n# 写回文件\nwith open('src/advanced/function.py', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    f.write(content)\n\nprint(\"Done\")","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\fix_function_v708.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":147094,"output":2377,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":149471,"cost":{"input":0.147094,"output":0.007606400000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.15470040000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781433978059,"responseId":"cht000d5159@dx19ec5bd4e8fb8ab282"}}
