{"type":"message","id":"c997261e","parentId":"7db53217","timestamp":"2026-06-14T10:58:46.536Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-2b1dcb557c404eb883430f3cb84448ac","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def disconnect_device(self, ip: str) -> None:\r\n        \"\"\"v6.30: 断开设备连接。清除 active_device，保留 last_connected 用于下次快速连接。\"\"\"\r\n        self._controllers.pop(ip, None)\r\n        client = self._clients.pop(ip, None)\r\n        if client:\r\n            try:\r\n                client.session.close()\r\n            except Exception:\r\n                pass\r\n        \r\n        # 更新设备状态\r\n        ptz_cfg = self.config.load_ptz_config()\r\n        disconnected_mac = None\r\n        for key, dev in ptz_cfg.get(\"devices\", {}).items():\r\n            if dev.get(\"ip\") == ip:\r\n                dev[\"connected\"] = False\r\n                disconnected_mac = key\r\n                self.config.save_ptz_config(ptz_cfg)\r\n                break\r\n        \r\n        # v6.31: 清除 active_device，保留 last_connected\r\n        if disconnected_mac:\r\n            try:\r\n                registry_file = self.config._registry_file\r\n                if registry_file.exists():\r\n                    registry = json.loads(registry_file.read_text(encoding='utf-8'))\r\n                    if registry.get('active_device') == disconnected_mac:\r\n                        registry['active_device'] = \"\"\r\n                        # last_connected 保留不变\r\n                        _atomic_write(registry_file, registry)\r\n                        LOG.log(\"info\", f\"registry.json active_device cleared for {disconnected_mac}, last_connected preserved\")\r\n            except Exception as e:\r\n                LOG.log(\"warning\", f\"更新 registry.json 失败: {e}\")\r\n\r\n    def list_controllers(self) -> list[str]:\r\n        return list(self._controllers.keys())\r\n\r\n    def is_device_connected(self, ip: str) -> bool:\r\n        return ip in self._controllers\r\n\r\n    def get_connected_device(self) -> dict | None:\r\n        \"\"\"v6.30: 从 registry.json 读取 last_connected 用于快速连接。\"\"\"\r\n        import json\r\n        from src.config_paths import REGISTRY_FILE, DEVICES_DIR\r\n        \r\n        try:\r\n            # 读取 registry.json\r\n            if REGISTRY_FILE.exists():\r\n                registry = json.loads(REGISTRY_FILE.read_text(encoding='utf-8'))\r\n                last_mac = registry.get('last_connected')\r\n                if not last_mac:\r\n                    return None\r\n                \r\n                # 从 devices/{mac}/info.json 读取设备详情\r\n                info_file = DEVICES_DIR / last_mac / 'info.json'\r\n                if info_file.exists():\r\n                    info = json.loads(info_file.read_text(encoding='utf-8'))\r\n                    # v6.17: 兼容 credentials 对象和根级别字段\r\n                    creds = info.get('credentials', {})\r\n                    return {\r\n                        'ip': info.get('ip'),\r\n                        'mac': last_mac,\r\n                        'name': info.get('name'),\r\n                        'model': info.get('model'),\r\n                        'username': creds.get('username') or info.get('username'),\r\n                        'password': creds.get('password') or info.get('password'),\r\n                        'port': info.get('port', 80),\r\n                        'device_name': info.get('device_name'),\r\n                    }\r\n        except Exception as e:\r\n            print(f'[PTZManager] get_connected_device error: {e}')\r\n        \r\n        return None\r\n\r\n    # ================================================================\r\n    #  设备信息获取\r\n    # ================================================================\r\n\r\n    def get_device_info(self, ip: str) -> dict:\r\n        \"\"\"通过 ISAPI 获取设备详细信息。\"\"\"\r\n\n[1154 more lines in file. Use offset=1754 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781434726536}}
{"type":"message","id":"bbc3d51b","parentId":"c997261e","timestamp":"2026-06-14T10:59:05.932Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**问题发现**：\n\n`get_connected_device()` 读取的是 `last_connected`，而不是检查设备是否实际连接！\n\n逻辑错误：\n- `disconnect_device()` 清除了 `active_device`，但保留了 `last_connected`\n- `get_connected_device()` 读取 `last_connected`，只要它存在就返回设备信息\n- **结果**：断开后，`last_connected` 还在，所以 `connected: true`\n\n正确逻辑应该是：\n1. `get_connected_device()` 应该检查 `active_device` 是否为空\n2. 或者检查 `_controllers` 中是否有该设备\n\n让我修复 `get_connected_device()` 方法："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_049073b5bb0b40bf982d4718","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def get_connected_device(self) -> dict | None:\n        \"\"\"v7.09: 从 registry.json 读取 active_device，检查是否实际连接。\"\"\"\n        import json\n        from src.config_paths import REGISTRY_FILE, DEVICES_DIR\n        \n        try:\n            # v7.09: 优先检查 active_device\n            if REGISTRY_FILE.exists():\n                registry = json.loads(REGISTRY_FILE.read_text(encoding='utf-8'))\n                active_mac = registry.get('active_device', '').strip()\n                \n                # v7.09: active_device 为空表示没有连接\n                if not active_mac:\n                    return None\n                \n                # 从 devices/{mac}/info.json 读取设备详情\n                info_file = DEVICES_DIR / active_mac / 'info.json'\n                if info_file.exists():\n                    info = json.loads(info_file.read_text(encoding='utf-8'))\n                    # v6.17: 兼容 credentials 对象和根级别字段\n                    creds = info.get('credentials', {})\n                    return {\n                        'ip': info.get('ip'),\n                        'mac': active_mac,\n                        'name': info.get('name'),\n                        'model': info.get('model'),\n                        'username': creds.get('username') or info.get('username'),\n                        'password': creds.get('password') or info.get('password'),\n                        'port': info.get('port', 80),\n                        'device_name': info.get('device_name'),\n                    }\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f'[PTZManager] get_connected_device error: {e}')\n        \n        return None","oldText":"    def get_connected_device(self) -> dict | None:\n        \"\"\"v6.30: 从 registry.json 读取 last_connected 用于快速连接。\"\"\"\n        import json\n        from src.config_paths import REGISTRY_FILE, DEVICES_DIR\n        \n        try:\n            # 读取 registry.json\n            if REGISTRY_FILE.exists():\n                registry = json.loads(REGISTRY_FILE.read_text(encoding='utf-8'))\n                last_mac = registry.get('last_connected')\n                if not last_mac:\n                    return None\n                \n                # 从 devices/{mac}/info.json 读取设备详情\n                info_file = DEVICES_DIR / last_mac / 'info.json'\n                if info_file.exists():\n                    info = json.loads(info_file.read_text(encoding='utf-8'))\n                    # v6.17: 兼容 credentials 对象和根级别字段\n                    creds = info.get('credentials', {})\n                    return {\n                        'ip': info.get('ip'),\n                        'mac': last_mac,\n                        'name': info.get('name'),\n                        'model': info.get('model'),\n                        'username': creds.get('username') or info.get('username'),\n                        'password': creds.get('password') or info.get('password'),\n                        'port': info.get('port', 80),\n                        'device_name': info.get('device_name'),\n                    }\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f'[PTZManager] get_connected_device error: {e}')\n        \n        return None"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"za