{"type":"message","id":"1d78467a","parentId":"796575ff","timestamp":"2026-06-14T11:01:55.495Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2a2576acc6e64b50948519f5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function disconnectDevice(ip) {\r\n            // v6.54: 防止重复点击\r\n            if (_connectionOperationInProgress) {\r\n                showToast('warning', '请等待上一次操作完成');\r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n            _connectionOperationInProgress = true;\r\n\r\n            // 禁用连接按钮\r\n            if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(false);\r\n\r\n            showToast('info', '正在断开设备...');\r\n            // --- Stop PTZ position polling ---\r\n            if (window.stopPtzPositionPoll) window.stopPtzPositionPoll();\r\n            // --- Stop WASM video stream ---\r\n            if (window.wasmLogout) window.wasmLogout();\r\n            // v6.16: 清除 WASM 状态\r\n            if (window.updateWasmStatus) window.updateWasmStatus('disconnected');\r\n\r\n            // v6.54: 禁用主控台和高级功能\r\n            if (window.disableAllControls) window.disableAllControls('请先连接设备');\r\n\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/devices/' + ip + '/disconnect', null).then(function() {\r\n                showToast('success', '设备已断开: ' + ip);\r\n                addLog('info', '设备已断开: ' + ip);\r\n                // --- Clear global window.connectedDevice first, before refresh ---\r\n                if (window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip === ip) {\r\n                    window.connectedDevice = null;\r\n                    addLog('info', '已清除连接设备状态');\r\n                }\r\n                if (window.updateDeviceStatus) window.updateDeviceStatus();\r\n                refreshDevices();\r\n                refreshPtzDeviceList();\r\n                refreshAdvancedDeviceSelectors();\r\n                var panel = document.getElementById('deviceInfoPanel');\r\n                if (panel) panel.style.display = 'none';\r\n\r\n                _connectionOperationInProgress = false;\r\n                if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(true);\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                _connectionOperationInProgress = false;\r\n                if (window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled) window.setConnectionButtonsEnabled(true);\r\n                showToast('error', '断开异常: ' + e.message);\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        function deleteDevice(identifier) {\r\n            if (!confirm('确定删除设备 ' + identifier + '?')) return;\r\n            apiDelete('/api/v1/devices/' + identifier).then(function() {\r\n                showToast('success', '设备已删除');\r\n                addLog('info', '设备已删除: ' + identifier);\r\n\n[1425 more lines in file. Use offset=1463 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781434915494}}
{"type":"message","id":"ed17fd0d","parentId":"1d78467a","timestamp":"2026-06-14T11:02:06.729Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**确认**：前端 `disconnectDevice` 函数调用的 API 是正确的：\n\n```javascript\napiPost('/api/v1/devices/' + ip + '/disconnect', null)\n```\n\n这与后端路由匹配。\n\n---\n\n## v7.09 修复总结\n\n### 问题诊断\n\n1. **根本原因**：`get_connected_device()` 读取 `last_connected` 字段，而 `disconnect_device()` 只清除了 `active_device`，保留了 `last_connected`\n\n2. **表现**：断开后 API 返回 `connected: true`，因为 `last_connected` 还存在\n\n### 修复内容\n\n**文件**：`src/core/ptz_manager.py`\n\n**修改**：`get_connected_device()` 方法\n- **旧逻辑**：读取 `last_connected` 字段\n- **新逻辑**：读取 `active_device` 字段，如果为空则返回 `None`\n\n### 测试结果\n\n```\n断开前: connected=true\n断开后: connected=false ✅\n```\n\n### 文件修改\n\n- `src/main/constants.py` - v7.09\n- `src/web/index.html` - v7.09\n- `src/core/ptz_manager.py` - 修复 get_connected_device 逻辑\n\n### 备份\n\n- `backup_20260614_v709/`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":71131,"output":280,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71411,"cost":{"input":0.071131,"output":0.0008960000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.072027}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781434915497,"responseId":"cht000de456@dx19ec5cb9c7db894142"}}
