{"type":"message","id":"bbb5b9b6","parentId":"11e36ee5","timestamp":"2026-06-14T11:32:55.361Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**完美！** \n\n---\n\n## v7.10 修复总结\n\n### 问题\n\nv7.09 的修改导致断开后快速连接无法使用，因为 `get_connected_device()` 读取 `active_device`，断开后被清空。\n\n### 正确逻辑\n\n| 场景 | `active_device` | `last_connected` | API 返回 |\n|------|-----------------|------------------|----------|\n| 已连接 | 有值 | 有值 | `{connected: true, device: {...}}` |\n| 断开后 | 空 | 有值（保留） | `{connected: false, device: {...}}` |\n| 从未连接 | 空 | 空 | `{connected: false, device: null}` |\n\n### 修改内容\n\n1. **ptz_manager.py** - `get_connected_device()`\n   - 恢复读取 `last_connected`（用于快速连接）\n\n2. **router.py** - `GET /ptz/connected`\n   - 新增：检查 `active_device` 判断 `connected` 状态\n   - 返回 `last_connected` 设备信息（即使未连接）\n\n### 测试结果\n\n```\n断开后:\n  connected: false ✅\n  device: {ip: 192.168.5.72, ...} ✅\n\n快速连接可用 ✅\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":75966,"output":280,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76246,"cost":{"input":0.07596599999999999,"output":0.0008960000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.07686199999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781436754147,"responseId":"cht000d0490@dx19ec5e7cedcba5c342"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b410680d","parentId":"bbb5b9b6","timestamp":"2026-06-14T11:55:03.642Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-06-14 19:53:43 GMT+8] Exec completed (grand-fj, code 0) :: NFO: 127.0.0.1:46900 - \"GET /api/v1/devices HTTP/1.1\" 200 OK INFO: 127.0.0.1:43595 - \"GET /api/v1/devices HTTP/1.1\" 200 OK INFO: 127.0.0.1:56401 - \"GET /api/v1/devices HTTP/1.1\" 2…\n\nAn async command you ran earlier has completed. The result is shown in the system messages above. Handle the result internally. Do not relay it to the user unless explicitly requested.\nCurrent time: Sunday, June 14th, 2026 - 19:54 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-06-14 11:54 UTC"}],"timestamp":1781438103636}}
{"type":"message","id":"f89f7d77","parentId":"b410680d","timestamp":"2026-06-14T11:55:14.210Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到。服务正常运行。\n\n---\n\n## v7.10 修复完成\n\n**核心修复**：\n\n| 方法 | 读取字段 | 用途 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| `get_connected_device()` | `last_connected` | 快速连接\"上次连的是谁\" |\n| `GET /ptz/connected` API | `active_device` | 判断\"当前是否在线\" |\n\n**API 返回**：\n\n```json\n// 断开后\n{\n  \"connected\": false,      // active_device 为空\n  \"device\": {...}          // last_connected 保留\n}\n```\n\n快速连接功能现已恢复正常。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":76344,"output":134,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76478,"cost":{"input":0.076344,"output":0.0004288,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0767728}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781438103643,"responseId":"cht000eb54b@dx19ec5fc4e83b893102"}}
