{"type":"message","id":"0e473f25","parentId":"60107a1b","timestamp":"2026-06-14T12:44:27.485Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"断开成功。\n\n---\n\n## v7.11 修复总结\n\n### 问题\n\n断开连接后，画面控制的增益控件未禁用，仍可操作。\n\n### 修复内容\n\n**文件**：`src/web/includes/console.html`\n\n**修改**：`disableImageControls()` 和 `enableImageControls()` 函数\n\n- 在控件列表中添加 `'gainLevel'`\n\n### 修改代码\n\n```javascript\n// v7.11: 添加 gainLevel\nvar controls = [\n    'consoleBrightness', 'consoleContrast', 'consoleSaturation', 'consoleSharpness',\n    'wbMode', 'wbRed', 'wbBlue', 'dnrSpatial', 'dnrTemporal',\n    'exposureMode', 'shutterSpeed', 'irisLevel', 'gainLevel',  // v7.11: 添加\n    'infoOsdSwitch', 'ptzOsdSwitch'\n];\n```\n\n### 测试结果\n\n断开后：\n- 增益控件 disabled ✅\n- OSD 控件 disabled ✅\n- PTZ 按钮 disabled ✅"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":82452,"output":225,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82677,"cost":{"input":0.082452,"output":0.00072,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.083172}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781441046680,"responseId":"cht000df92d@dx19ec6294733b87f702"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7c51d3c","parentId":"0e473f25","timestamp":"2026-06-14T13:17:44.688Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write any lasting notes to memory/2026-06-14.md; reply with the exact silent token NO_REPLY if nothing to store.\n\nStore durable memories only in memory/2026-06-14.md (create memory/ if needed).\n\nIf memory/2026-06-14.md already exists, APPEND new content only and do not overwrite existing entries.\n\nTreat workspace bootstrap/reference files such as MEMORY.md, DREAMS.md, SOUL.md, TOOLS.md, and AGENTS.md as read-only during this flush; never overwrite, replace, or edit them.\nCurrent time: Sunday, June 14th, 2026 - 21:17 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-06-14 13:17 UTC"}],"timestamp":1781443064684}}
{"type":"message","id":"f32aab2a","parentId":"e7c51d3c","timestamp":"2026-06-14T13:18:21.460Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d681eb26d03140de9e8593f6","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"memory/2026-06-14.md","content":"# 2026-06-14 Memory\n\n## v7.07 - 快门/光圈独立端点修复\n\n### 问题\n设置快门时光圈也被修改，因为快门和光圈都通过 Exposure 端点传递。\n\n### 正确逻辑\n- **曝光模式**: `/exposure` + `<ExposureType>manual</ExposureType>`\n- **快门**: `/Shutter` + `<ShutterLevel>` (独立端点，只接受特定值如 1/25, 1/250, 1/1000)\n- **光圈**: `/Iris` + `<IrisLevel>` (独立端点)\n\n### 测试结果\n- 设置手动模式: 200 ✅\n- 设置快门 1/250: 200 ✅\n- 设置光圈 1600: 200 ✅\n\n---\n\n## v7.08 - 从 capabilities 端点获取 opt_values\n\n### 问题\n快门下拉列表硬编码，不从设备获取实际可选值。\n\n### 修复\n1. 添加 `_parse_opt_values()` 方法解析 XML 的 opt 属性\n2. 添加 `_fetch_capabilities_opt_values()` 方法调用 `/Image/channels/1/capabilities`\n3. 修改 `FunctionResult` 添加 `opt_values` 字段\n4. 修改前端 `loadShutter()` 和 `loadIris()` 使用 opt_values\n\n### 测试结果\n```\n快门 opt_values: ['1/25', '1/50', '1/75', '1/100', ...]\n光圈 opt_values: ['160', '200', '240', '280', ...]\n```\n\n---\n\n## v7.09 - 断开后状态显示修复（错误版本）\n\n### 问题\n断开后 `/ptz/connected` 仍返回 `connected: true`。\n\n### 错误修复\n把 `get_connected_device()` 改成读 `active_device`，导致快速连接失效。\n\n---\n\n## v7.10 - 正确修复断开状态\n\n### 问题\nv7.09 导致断开后快速连接显示\"无上次连接设备\"。\n\n### 正确逻辑\n| 状态 | active_device | last_connected | API 返回 |\n|------|---------------|----------------|----------|\n| 已连接 | 有值 | 有值 | `{connected: true, device: {...}}` |\n| 断开后 | 空 | 有值（保留） | `{connected: false, device: {...}}` |\n| 从未连接 | 空 | 空 | `{connected: false, device: null}` |\n\n### 字段区别\n- **active_device**: 当前在用设备，断开就清空\n- **last_connected**: 上次用过设备，断开不清空，保留记忆\n\n### 修改\n1. `get_connected_device()` 读取 `last_connected`（用于快速连接）\n2. `GET /ptz/connected` API 检查 `active_device` 判断 `connected` 状态\n\n---\n\n## v7.11 - 断开后控件禁用修复\n\n### 问题\n断开连接后，增益控件仍可操作。\n\n### 修复\n在 `disableImageControls()` 控件列表中添加 `'gainLevel'`。\n\n### 测试结果\n断开后所有控件正确禁用：增益、OSD、PTZ 按钮。\n\n---\n\n## 关键学习\n\n### 设备状态字段\n```\nactive_device  = \"当前在用\"  → 断开就清空\nlast_connected = \"上次用过\" → 断开不清空，保留记忆\n```\n\n### 快速连接逻辑\n- 打开开关 → 读 `last_connected` 找上次设备\n- API 查询状态 → 读 `active_device` 判断是否在线\n\n### ISAPI 端点分离\n海康设备的快门、光圈必须使用独立端点，不能混用 Exposure 端点。\n\n### Shutter opt_values\nShutter 端点只接受特定值，从 capabilities 端点获取 opt 列表。\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":50524,"output":872,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51396,"cost":{"input":0.050524,"output":0.0027904,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0533144}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781443064689,"responseId":"cht000d222a@dx19ec6484024ba5d322"}}
