{"type":"message","id":"57ba4cdb","parentId":"74ef6b1b","timestamp":"2026-06-14T13:23:36.255Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**测试通过！** \n\n- 无上次设备时显示 toast：\"无上次连接设备,请执行发现流程\"\n\n---\n\n## v7.12 修复总结\n\n### 问题\n\n刷新页面后提示\"无上次连接设备\"，但实际上 `last_connected` 有值。\n\n### 根本原因\n\n`restoreConnectionState()` 函数只检查 `!r.connected`，没有区分：\n- `!r.connected && r.device` → 有上次设备\n- `!r.connected && !r.device` → 无上次设备\n\n### 正确逻辑\n\n| 状态 | API 返回 | 前端行为 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| 已连接 | `connected: true, device: {...}` | 恢复连接状态 |\n| 有上次设备（未连接） | `connected: false, device: {...}` | **自动连接** |\n| 无上次设备 | `connected: false, device: null` | 提示\"执行发现流程\" |\n\n### 修复内容\n\n**文件**：`src/web/index.html`\n\n**修改**：`restoreConnectionState()` 函数\n\n添加分支：\n```javascript\n} else if (r && r.success && !r.connected && r.device) {\n    // v7.12: 未连接但有上次设备 → 自动连接\n    window.connectDevice(r.device.ip);\n}\n```\n\n### 测试结果\n\n- ✅ 有上次设备 → 自动连接\n- ✅ 无上次设备 → 显示提示"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":89000,"output":305,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89305,"cost":{"input":0.089,"output":0.0009760000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.089976}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781443385697,"responseId":"cht000df23e@dx19ec64d2c43ba5e412"}}
