{"type":"message","id":"4b39a788","parentId":"f3f9eb37","timestamp":"2026-06-14T14:45:07.398Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 复盘完成\n\n**核心收获**：\n\n1. **状态字段必须语义清晰** - active_device vs last_connected\n2. **ISAPI 端点分离原则** - 快门/光圈/曝光模式各自独立\n3. **前端状态恢复三分支** - 已连接/有设备/无设备\n4. **清理前必查依赖** - grep → 注释 → 删除 → 验证"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":138872,"output":93,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138965,"cost":{"input":0.138872,"output":0.0002976,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1391696}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781448296397,"responseId":"cht000d0a1f@dx19ec697cfc6b85f582"}}
